# ROOZER Privacy Policy

Effective Date: April 2026

ROOZER ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled within the ROOZER app.

## Information We Collect

ROOZER uses the following device features:

### Camera (TrueDepth / ARKit)

The app uses the device camera to enable real-time face tracking for gameplay. This includes detecting:

* Eye movement
* Facial expressions (winks, mouth movement, eyebrows, cheeks)
* Head position

This data is processed in real time on your device only.

We do NOT:

* Record video or images
* Store face data
* Upload face data to servers
* Share face data with third parties

### Microphone

The app uses the microphone for gameplay features such as voice-based interactions (e.g., singing or sound detection in Tone Deaf).

We do NOT:

* Record audio
* Store audio recordings
* Upload audio data
* Share audio data with third parties

## Data Storage

All processing occurs locally on your device. No biometric or audio data is stored or transmitted.

## Third-Party Services

ROOZER does not use third-party analytics, advertising SDKs, or external data collection services.

## Children’s Privacy

ROOZER does not knowingly collect personal data from children. All gameplay data remains on-device.

